      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a strong shine with only minor surface scratches and small rock chips consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing some light wear on the driver's seat bolster but otherwise free of tears or odors. Mechanically, the car performs well, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has received regular oil changes. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that is ready for the road.",
