    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty! I've babied this car since day one, and it's still in totally pristine, showroom condition. It looks and smells brand new, and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm honestly a little sad to let it go, but I'm looking for a great new home for it. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in perfect shape, this is the one for you! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
