    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3, a turn-key example of high-revving atmospheric performance. The S54 3.2L inline-six remains the centerpiece, featuring perfectly calibrated individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system with zero timing deviation. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings, addressing the chassis's critical stress points. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and linear torque delivery. The suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances, with Bilstein dampers maintaining optimal rebound and compression characteristics. An investment-grade vehicle for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
