      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade masterpiece that remains in showroom condition. Meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. The interior is equally breathtaking, featuring untouched leather that retains its factory-fresh scent and original matte texture, with zero wear on the bolsters or controls. Every button, screen, and mechanical component operates with the precision of a new vehicle. Accompanied by a full, documented service history and recent professional detailing, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. It is a true time capsule, ready for the most discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
